extends ../base

block content
  p “Cron jobs” are what developers write to schedule tasks. They're hard to remember. So!{' '}
    a(href="https://cronitor.io/" target="_blank")
      span.italic Cronitor
    |!{' '}made a little side project to help.
  p Developers search “Cron job every [time interval]”. And!{' '}
    a(href="https://crontab.guru/" target="_blank")
      span.italic Crontab
    |!{' '}(the little side project) gives you the code to copy and paste. Lovely.
  img(src="https://ik.imagekit.io/o08ysq9vx/newsletters/nl4/nl2f.png" alt="Crontab Guru SEO").img__90
  p Now, there's 100's of possible time intervals (meaning 100's of possible keywords).!{' '}
    span.italic Crontab
    |!{' '}has a new page for every single one.
  img(src="https://ik.imagekit.io/o08ysq9vx/newsletters/nl4/nl2d.png" alt="Crontab Guru Search Volumes").img__90
  p It's a ridiculously simple site. Pulling in
    span.italic 120k organic traffic/mo
    | . Lightly promoting their paid tool.
  p How to replicate? Well, you're looking for:
  p.inwardSpeech A group of!{' '}
    span.bold similar questions
    | . That your customers are googling. That you can answer with!{' '}
    span.bold one template.
  p
    span.italic h/t!{' '}
      a(href="https://twitter.com/PierreDeWulf") Pierre de Wulf
  p
    span.italic — Harry